name: Data Anonymization with Presidio
description:
Use this template to anonymize PII data from text files during copy between one storage account to another, with Presidio.  

The pipeline enumerates the files on the input blob container, reads their content and sends it to predefined presidio endpoints for analysis and anonymization before writing them back to the new blob container.  

Note that you should first follow through with the required provisioning steps in the documentation link for the template to work.
author: Microsoft
